<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description>龙龙的技术博客</description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/rss.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2017 14:20:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>CAD练习题15--利用平行四边形画不规则多边形3</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-15-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-3/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题的方法与 &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-13-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-1/"&gt;https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-13-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-1/&lt;/a&gt; 也是一致的，只是多了一个平移，当然这里的做法不止这一种。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先分别画已知的部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-1.PNG"&gt;https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-1.PNG&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、平移到一起。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-2.PNG"&gt;https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-2.PNG&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、作平行四边形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-3.PNG"&gt;https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-3.PNG&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-4.PNG"&gt;https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-4.PNG&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-5.PNG"&gt;https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-5.PNG&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-6.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-15-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-3/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2017 14:16:20 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题14——利用平行四边形画不规则多边形2</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-14-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-2/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p14-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p14-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题的方法与 &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-13-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-1/"&gt;https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-13-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-1/&lt;/a&gt; 是一致的。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画已知部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p14-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p14-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、构造平行四边形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p14-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p14-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p14-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p14-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p14-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p14-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p14-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p14-5.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-14-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-2/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2017 12:51:28 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题13——利用平行四边形画不规则多边形1</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-13-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-1/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p13-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p13-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题看上去不难，但是画到上边斜线的时候就需要想一下从哪里下手了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画外边的三角形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p13-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p13-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、构造一个平行四边形，在底边构造一条和上边斜线平行并且一样长的线，然后利用平行四边形对边平行且相等，平移到目标位置。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p13-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p13-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p13-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p13-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p13-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p13-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p13-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p13-5.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-13-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-1/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2017 12:33:37 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>win10下仅允许一个程序联网，并禁止其他所有程序联网</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/win10xia-jin-yun-xu-yi-ge-cheng-xu-lian-wang-bing-jin-zhi-qi-ta-suo-you-cheng-xu-lian-wang/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;当电脑共享手机热点上网时，为避免浪费流量，就需要设置只让我们需要的程序联网，使用win10自带的防火墙，可以设置所有程序都不能联网，但是无法设置只让一个程序联网。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TinyWall（&lt;a class="reference external" href="http://tinywall.pados.hu/"&gt;http://tinywall.pados.hu/&lt;/a&gt;）可以解决这个问题。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;安装好之后，启动要允许联网的程序，右击托盘图标，点击"管理"，“应用程序例外”，“添加应用程序”，“选择进程”即可。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>win10</category><category>防火墙</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/win10xia-jin-yun-xu-yi-ge-cheng-xu-lian-wang-bing-jin-zhi-qi-ta-suo-you-cheng-xu-lian-wang/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2017 12:02:14 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>业罢伤秋</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ye-ba-shang-qiu/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;冬临万木枝灿灿，秋扫街头叶翩翩。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;枯蒿处处无颜色，干草丛丛有碧澜。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;北风易夺世间暖，艳阳难愈天下寒。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;凄凄大地行人少，历历乾坤一片蓝。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>我的诗词</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ye-ba-shang-qiu/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2017 15:19:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题12——已知过一点和相切圆画圆</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-12-yi-zhi-guo-yi-dian-he-wai-qie-yuan-hua-yuan/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-7.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题知道圆过点、相切圆、半径，既不符合相切相切半径、也不符合三边相切。那么怎么画呢？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画已知的部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、由于过一点又知道半径，那么我们从这一点为圆心画圆，目标弧的圆心一定在这个圆上。同时又知道外切圆，所以圆心之间连线长度等于半径之和，所以一个圆半径是35，一个圆半径是50，总长度是85。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、上一步中两个圆的交点就是目标弧的圆心。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、同样的画法来画左边的80，但是注意这个是内切圆了，所以半径是减法，一个圆半径是80，一个圆半径是35，总长度是45。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-7.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-12-yi-zhi-guo-yi-dian-he-wai-qie-yuan-hua-yuan/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2017 11:47:14 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题11——利用平行和偏移作三角形内接花型图案</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-11-li-yong-ping-xing-he-pian-yi-zuo-san-jiao-xing-nei-jie-hua-xing-tu-an/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-8.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-8.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题看上去很难入手，先画三角形吧，不好找到内切的位置；先画花吧，不好找到外切的位置……&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画三角形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、利用五边形画花。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、过五边形左右两个顶点和底边顶点，分别作三角形三边的平行线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、利用圆的半径，偏移上一步中的三条直线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6、缩放图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-7.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-11-li-yong-ping-xing-he-pian-yi-zuo-san-jiao-xing-nei-jie-hua-xing-tu-an/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2017 11:16:45 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题10——利用平行作三角形的近似内接多边形</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-10-li-yong-ping-xing-zuo-san-jiao-xing-de-jin-si-nei-jie-duo-bian-xing/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题很容易想到画三角形的内切圆，但是得不到目标图形。所以，我们采用平行加缩放来作图。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画出三角形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、从旁边画出五边形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、过五边形上边两个顶点和底边顶点，分别作三角形三条边的平行线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、缩放图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-5.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-10-li-yong-ping-xing-zuo-san-jiao-xing-de-jin-si-nei-jie-duo-bian-xing/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2017 11:10:53 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题9——较为复杂的利用圆作固定角度三角形</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-9-jiao-wei-fu-za-de-li-yong-yuan-zuo-gu-ding-jiao-du-san-jiao-xing/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-12.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-12.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题看上去较为复杂，但实际上还是利用圆作固定角度三角形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、画出明显已知的部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、画出下半部分的90度。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、作等分和旋转作垂线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、先处理右侧的72度，由于顶角是72度，所以作一条18度的斜线和过基线中点的垂线，以相交的点为圆心画圆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、上一步的圆与最右侧垂线交于一点，连接三点，得到72度顶角。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6、同样原理，得到其他三个角，注意每次基线长度是不同的。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-7.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-8.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-8.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-9.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-9.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-10.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-10.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-11.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-11.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-12.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-12.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-9-jiao-wei-fu-za-de-li-yong-yuan-zuo-gu-ding-jiao-du-san-jiao-xing/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2017 11:01:53 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题8——利用圆作直角三角形和固定角度三角形</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-8-li-yong-yuan-zuo-zhi-jiao-san-jiao-xing-he-gu-ding-jiao-du-san-jiao-xing/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-8.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-8.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题的难点在于怎么画下面的90度和上面的75度，我们将用圆来解决这个问题。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、画出明显已知的部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、利用直角三角形斜边中线等于斜边一半的原理，以斜边为直径画圆，确定直角的位置。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、作出等分点和垂线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、因为顶角是75度，作一条与基线是呈15度的斜线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、在基线的中点作一条垂线，与上一步中的斜线相交于一点，过这点画圆，与第3步中的垂线交于一点。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6、连接三个已知点，得到75度顶角。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-7.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-8-li-yong-yuan-zuo-zhi-jiao-san-jiao-xing-he-gu-ding-jiao-du-san-jiao-xing/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2017 10:45:54 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>